{"tha-ap177:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap177:0.2":"Kumudavagga ","tha-ap177:0.3":"Sihasanadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap177:1.1":"“Nibbute lokanathamhi, ","tha-ap177:1.2":"padumuttaranayake; ","tha-ap177:1.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap177:1.4":"sihasanamadasaham. ","tha-ap177:2.1":"Bahuhi gandhamalehi, ","tha-ap177:2.2":"ditthadhammasukhavahe; ","tha-ap177:2.3":"Tattha pujanca katvana, ","tha-ap177:2.4":"nibbayati bahujjano. ","tha-ap177:3.1":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap177:3.2":"vanditva bodhimuttamam; ","tha-ap177:3.3":"Kappanam satasahassam, ","tha-ap177:3.4":"duggatim nupapajjaham. ","tha-ap177:4.1":"Pannarasasahassamhi, ","tha-ap177:4.2":"kappanam attha asu te; ","tha-ap177:4.3":"Siluccayasanama ca, ","tha-ap177:4.4":"rajano cakkavattino. ","tha-ap177:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap177:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap177:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap177:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sihasanadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap177:7.1":"Sihasanadayakattherassapadanam pancamam. "}